-- KKR says offer period for WMF bid runs until Aug. 11
-- By Christoph Steitz
-- Mon Jul 14, 2014 03:47AM EDT
-- None



FRANKFURT, July 14 (Reuters) - KKR <KKR.N> said holders of preferred shares in German cutlery and coffee machines maker WMF <WMFG.F> <WMFG_p.F> have until Aug. 11 to accept a 53-euro ($72.29) per share offer from the U.S. buyout firm, KKR said in a statement on Monday. ($1 = 0.7331 Euros)   (Reporting by Christoph Steitz; Editing by Ludwig Burger)  ((christoph.steitz@thomsonreuters.com)(+49 69 7565 1269)(Reuters Messaging: christoph.steitz.thomsonreuters.com@reuters.net))  Keywords: WMF KKR/MERGERS

